name: EMillion X Silvertool Gold
description:
PREMIUM SKATEBOARD TOOL
The EMillion X Silver Skateboard Tool is the perfect tool for complete skateboard assembly with versatile features and maximum durability.

FEATURES:
- 3/8 Inch Socket with PATENTED EXCLUSIVE RATCHET 
  capabilities - adjust your hardware with the greatest of ease

- 9/16 Inch Socket - easily tighten or loosen your trucks

- 1/2 Inch Socket - comfortably add, remove and secure your wheels

- Removable Screwdriver - slide out reversible phillips and allenhead driver

- Precision File - double cut medium grade file for a smooth griptape edge

- Detachable Allen Key - 5mm magnetic allen attachment accomodates trucks with allenhead kingpins
